summary: Fixed Taarie so she doesn\'t look like the ugly tree.
descriptionHtml:
There\'s no arguing it, Taarie is just flat-out fugly... period.  This is a simple reskin to make her more attractive.  I didn\'t change anything other than her face and hair.

Installation:
Drop the meshes folder and the esp into your data folder.

Required Mods:
ApachiiSkyHair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168

If you want her to look exactly like the pictures:
Better Females By Bella - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812
Human Eyes for Elves - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/195
CBBEv3 Big Bottom Edition - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666

I want to give credit to all the modders who make small-time guys like me look good.  :D

Thanks to:
Caliente
Porcelyn
BellaGail
apachii

Without your hard work, none of this would matter!
author: DDey
